\b it takes care of current edit step
\b0 . So you can setup quickly precise and easy shuffle (There is the {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://forum.renoise.com/index.php/topic/26692-new-tools-iterative-quantize-and-groove-tool/?p=350260"}}{\fldrslt \cf3 \ul \ulc3 groove tool}}, which is great). Using this, you can quickly setup a shuffle, relative to your current values. \
